divs: Sighting DetailsWatching for shooting stars and saw a pin point object traveling north to south. Object approached two parallel air liners flying two miles apart. Object increased in brightness until it appeared to be as large as a nickle. It moved within three miles of jets then disappeared. Light was very intense.
Summary: Star like object at high altitude
